WEBVTT

00:00:03.049 --> 00:00:06.198
THIS IS TAPE NUMBER SIX OF AN INTERVIEW

00:00:06.289 --> 00:00:08.223
WITH NORA BOGOT

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:12.324
ON MARCH SECOND, NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN IN BROOKLINE, MASSACHUSETTS

00:00:12.330 --> 00:00:13.826
AND I'M MARK DAVID

00:00:13.967 --> 00:00:14.872
NORA

00:00:15.047 --> 00:00:16.307
itster kumt

00:00:15.739 --> 00:00:17.386
bafrayt

00:00:16.307 --> 00:00:19.767
kumen mir tsu der bafrayung. eyn, eyn ah frage hob ikh gehat

00:00:19.767 --> 00:00:21.467
a- az di, di

00:00:21.467 --> 00:00:23.497
ungerishe un rumenishe

00:00:23.248 --> 00:00:25.064
geven mit mir tsuzamen

00:00:23.549 --> 00:00:25.087
yidn zaynen gekumen

00:00:25.087 --> 00:00:28.020
fun vanet zaynen zey gekumen? fun andere arbets lagern?

00:00:26.944 --> 00:00:29.013
zey kumen fun, fun STUTTHOF.

00:00:29.425 --> 00:00:31.511
fun STUTTHOF hot men zey genumen oyf arbet.

00:00:31.618 --> 00:00:33.299
bay undz iz geven ungarishe.

00:00:33.593 --> 00:00:37.350
zey hobn geredt, ze- zey hobn, zey zaynen geven yidish redndike?

00:00:33.610 --> 00:00:34.836
un rumenishe

00:00:36.343 --> 00:00:38.817
yidishe, un frume meydlekh

00:00:38.689 --> 00:00:40.623
fun di Karpatn, veyst ⟨ir⟩?

00:00:39.668 --> 00:00:41.520
fun di Karpatn, fun di ⟨erter⟩.

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:43.390
zey zaynen geven zeyer frume religyeze.

00:00:43.390 --> 00:00:45.090
zey hobn gevust oyfn zun

00:00:45.090 --> 00:00:47.697
hobn zey gevust ven s'iz yontev, ven s'iz yomkiper.

00:00:47.697 --> 00:00:49.011
keyner hot nit gegesn.

00:00:49.135 --> 00:00:51.069
zey hobn undz ongezogt az haynt iz yomkiper.

00:00:51.126 --> 00:00:52.892
oyfn zun hobn zey farshtanen.

00:00:53.083 --> 00:00:54.849
geven zey fun religyeze heymen.

00:00:54.906 --> 00:00:57.650
yunge, akhtsn yorike, zaynen ale gefaln.

00:00:57.758 --> 00:00:59.068
zey hobn nit gekent oyshaltn.

00:00:59.310 --> 00:01:02.775
in di grobn UNK ⟨zey zaynen⟩ geshtanen in, in di okopes grobn

00:01:02.775 --> 00:01:08.062
zaynen zey geshtanen. eyne iz geven a mey- meydl vos zi hot gehat a halbe kop iz geven gro un a halbe shvarts.

00:01:08.372 --> 00:01:09.885
akhtsn yorike.

00:01:09.975 --> 00:01:11.853
un s'iz geven andere, iz geven

00:01:11.853 --> 00:01:13.912
UNK ⟨mit⟩ a folk iz dokh do farsheydene

00:01:13.912 --> 00:01:15.963
artistishe, gekent zingen sheyn

00:01:15.963 --> 00:01:17.296
artistishe zakhn.

00:01:17.296 --> 00:01:20.027
andere geven gr- groyse gelernte meydlekh oykhet.

00:01:20.185 --> 00:01:24.476
un zey hobn gezogt azoy az ersht akht monatn ho- ⟨az⟩ m'hot zey gemakht

00:01:24.476 --> 00:01:26.518
UNK mit undz UNK gehat

00:01:26.518 --> 00:01:28.695
di dray yor, di fir yor, dem letstn

00:01:28.695 --> 00:01:30.354
dem letstn yor hobn zey dos

00:01:30.664 --> 00:01:33.547
un zey hobn ge- un zey hobn, dos ⟨hot men⟩ gezogt, un gezogt az

00:01:33.547 --> 00:01:36.287
az di kinder mit di eltern zaynen avek shoyn nokh AUSCHWITZ

00:01:36.520 --> 00:01:38.724
un di arbets feike kumen mit undz

00:01:39.270 --> 00:01:43.466
un zaynen geven UNK di lager firerke iz geven a ungarishe froy. ⟨ERINKA⟩ hot men ir geheysn.

00:01:43.557 --> 00:01:46.290
sheyne froy a, ⟨ERINKA, ERINKA⟩.

00:01:44.299 --> 00:01:45.896
vi hot zi geheysn?

00:01:46.290 --> 00:01:49.000
zi flegt es- oysshrayen az mir zoln oyfshteyn, me zol geyn

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.090
KAFFEHALL. zi flegt onfirn.

00:01:51.090 --> 00:01:53.420
un mit mir in barak iz oykh geven ungarishe un

00:01:53.420 --> 00:01:55.464
ungarishe merstnteyl un rumenishe.

00:01:55.504 --> 00:01:57.624
m'hot zey gebrakht in STUTTHOF

00:01:57.647 --> 00:01:59.585
di yunge oyf arbet, un UNK

00:01:59.585 --> 00:02:01.787
tates, UNK tate gehat ⟨khotsh⟩ a groysn bord

00:02:01.787 --> 00:02:03.272
mit finf kleyne kinderlekh.

00:02:03.272 --> 00:02:04.850
ale gegangen nokh AUSCHWITZ.

00:02:04.850 --> 00:02:06.180
ale, ale.

00:02:06.540 --> 00:02:08.272
un di yunge hobn nit gekent oyshaltn.

00:02:08.937 --> 00:02:11.074
zaynen geven azoyne shvakhe meydlekh.

00:02:11.755 --> 00:02:13.278
zey hobn nit gekent oyshaltn.

00:02:13.278 --> 00:02:16.409
zey flegn shteyn un loyzn zikh UNK in, in di grub

00:02:16.409 --> 00:02:19.499
di layz flegt zey esn, flegt zikh loyzn mit a k- mit a

00:02:19.499 --> 00:02:22.509
mit fayer mit a kinerl UNK di layz.

00:02:22.943 --> 00:02:24.053
zeyer sh-

00:02:24.053 --> 00:02:26.188
zeyer g- farlayzikt zaynen zey geven.

00:02:26.188 --> 00:02:26.989
shreklekh.

00:02:26.989 --> 00:02:28.724
di layz iz bafaln alemen.

00:02:29.406 --> 00:02:31.054
e- ale hobn dos gehat.

00:02:31.498 --> 00:02:34.267
un m'iz, eyn kleydl geven, eyn, ⟨mir hobn⟩ nit gehat UNK

00:02:34.267 --> 00:02:36.177
m'hot keyn vaser nit gegebn oyf vashn zikh oykh nit.

00:02:36.342 --> 00:02:37.866
a, a kulturele folk

00:02:37.866 --> 00:02:39.241
hot nit gegebn keyn vaser.

00:02:39.241 --> 00:02:40.219
shtelt zikh for.

00:02:40.219 --> 00:02:42.180
m'hot gegebn a tsvey liter

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:43.520
vaser heyse

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:45.440
zuntik f- dos flegt men undz gebn

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:47.793
vayl der n- s'iz gevorn farfrorn der taykhele.

00:02:47.884 --> 00:02:51.961
UNK un m'hot nit gegebn keyn UNK nit geven keyn antloyzung tsu geyn in a bod.

00:02:51.613 --> 00:02:59.690
di, di poylishe un litvishe dort hobn, zaynen oysgekumen mit di nay gekumene ungarishe

00:02:58.212 --> 00:03:01.803
m- mit di ungarish-, me, me flegt zikh krign oykhet.

00:03:01.803 --> 00:03:05.127
 me, me, ah, mit mir iz geven a ungarishe, rumenishe

00:03:05.127 --> 00:03:07.200
flegt zi hobn a sherl oyf shern di hor

00:03:07.223 --> 00:03:10.018
fleg betn bay ir borgn arumshern di, di negl

00:03:10.125 --> 00:03:12.830
flegt zi zogn az ikh zol nit esn mayn portsye broyt

00:03:12.830 --> 00:03:14.620
un batsoln ir, vet zi mir dan gebn.

00:03:14.833 --> 00:03:16.396
azoy hot zi nit gevelt gebn.

00:03:16.538 --> 00:03:19.010
iz az ikh ⟨fleg⟩ geyn tsu der arbet, hob ikh ir a mol gekhapt epes

00:03:19.010 --> 00:03:20.450
a UNK, veyst ir azoy

00:03:20.450 --> 00:03:25.352
a zise dos, fleg ikh ir shoyn gebn ot do, ikh hob mit mayn shvester gegesn eyn portsye

00:03:25.352 --> 00:03:28.153
un zuntik flegn mir gebn, zol zi gebn arumshern di negl.

00:03:28.153 --> 00:03:30.001
andere hobn dos ⟨nit⟩ gekrogn.

00:03:30.001 --> 00:03:31.146
m'hot zey gebrakht

00:03:31.168 --> 00:03:34.284
m'hot nit gegebn a nodl nit, keyn zakhn. m'hot nit gedarft gornisht nit.

00:03:34.425 --> 00:03:35.634
UNK geneyt

00:03:36.045 --> 00:03:37.946
a mentsh vert gornisht.

00:03:38.290 --> 00:03:39.836
azoy vi a ANIMAL vert er.

00:03:39.943 --> 00:03:41.320
a khaye, a khaye.

00:03:41.445 --> 00:03:42.890
a vilde khaye.

00:03:43.116 --> 00:03:45.306
m'hot nit gekukt oy- ikh fleg ibergeyn

00:03:45.306 --> 00:03:48.076
a froy iz gelegn a toyte, hob ikh ibergegangen iber ir

00:03:48.076 --> 00:03:49.836
un zi iz geshlofn lebn mir a gantse vokh.

00:03:49.836 --> 00:03:51.075
s'hot mir nit geart.

00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:53.859
m'hot nokh aropgetsoygn fun yede shikh andere

00:03:54.034 --> 00:03:55.597
un di zakhn fun ir.

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:57.825
s'hot nit geart gornisht nit.

00:03:58.050 --> 00:04:00.561
az ikh bin ge- azoy farhartevet vert men

00:04:00.561 --> 00:04:02.384
az s'interesirt zi gornisht nit.

00:04:02.384 --> 00:04:04.102
der lebn hot keyn vert nit.

00:04:04.075 --> 00:04:06.971
hot ir getrakht vegn religye demolt?

00:04:06.252 --> 00:04:08.762
reli- NO, NO, NO. keyn ⟨za-⟩

00:04:08.762 --> 00:04:10.542
me flegt zogn a mol betn bay got

00:04:10.542 --> 00:04:13.150
far vos shtroft men UNK, far vos, far vos

00:04:13.150 --> 00:04:14.593
helfstu undz nit, far vos

00:04:14.593 --> 00:04:16.702
un mir hot gezogt ober a daytshe yidene

00:04:16.702 --> 00:04:18.082
biz ikh bin geven in Zhezhmer

00:04:18.082 --> 00:04:20.381
a, a daytshisher soldat vos

00:04:20.381 --> 00:04:21.579
hot undz gehit

00:04:21.579 --> 00:04:23.761
az go- ir hot nit gehaltn gut di toyre

00:04:23.869 --> 00:04:25.719
got hot ir geshtroft zogt er

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:28.591
vayle m'hot gegebn tsu aykh di toyre, gut ⟨hot men⟩ gehaltn

00:04:28.591 --> 00:04:30.850
hot er aroys⟨geshikt⟩ melokhim aykh oyshargenen

00:04:30.850 --> 00:04:32.760
dernokh vet zayn far undz iz di zelbe zakh.

00:04:33.117 --> 00:04:34.393
er hot dos undz gezogt.

00:04:34.467 --> 00:04:37.903
az di, ven mir hobn geveynt az di, az m'hot umgebrakht di FAMILIES

00:04:37.926 --> 00:04:41.025
zogt er az got hot aykh geshtr- UNK gemakht.

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:43.505
er iz geven a religyezer daytsh

00:04:43.512 --> 00:04:45.289
zogt er "fun got kumt es."

00:04:45.289 --> 00:04:46.795
dos hot er undz ye gezogt.

00:04:48.135 --> 00:04:51.511
un, zey hobn gezogt a- az ir vet

00:04:51.511 --> 00:04:55.311
undz hot men gen- di, di vos zaynen shoyn gegangen nokh farn bafrayen

00:04:55.311 --> 00:04:57.631
hot er UNK dos iz geven in JANUARY

00:04:58.277 --> 00:05:00.290
nokh nay yor. s'iz in JANUARY

00:05:00.290 --> 00:05:06.034
i- mir hobn, me darf undz vekn tsu der arbet, az mir hobn geve- mir n- in di okopes hobn mir gedarft UNK di shney

00:05:06.141 --> 00:05:07.825
m'hot shoyn nit gegrobn keyn okopes.

00:05:07.825 --> 00:05:10.247
nor mir hobn gedarft aroysvarfn di shney fun di okopes

00:05:10.247 --> 00:05:11.839
un mir hobn gezen eroplanen

00:05:11.912 --> 00:05:13.374
in der heykh. hobn mir ale gekukt

00:05:13.650 --> 00:05:17.098
hobn andere meydlekh gezogt az dos iz nit keyn daytshishe eroplanen

00:05:17.098 --> 00:05:20.562
iz zet oys az s'iz fremde o- nit a- nit di eroplanen.

00:05:20.822 --> 00:05:23.282
iz di daytshn hobn gefregt vos kukn mir azoy vi

00:05:23.282 --> 00:05:27.464
nu mir, mir, UNK mir hobn nit gezogt gornisht nit

00:05:27.690 --> 00:05:31.076
dernokh hobn andere meydlekh gezogt az zey hobn gehert rusish me redt.

00:05:31.386 --> 00:05:32.792
epes ⟨do zaynen⟩ geven

00:05:32.792 --> 00:05:36.020
shoyn gehert dem rusish. mir hobn nit gegleybt az s'iz rikhtik

00:05:36.330 --> 00:05:38.689
un di daytshn hobn undz gezogt azoy

00:05:38.689 --> 00:05:41.693
az ver n- m'hot undz nit gevekt tsu der arbet

00:05:41.693 --> 00:05:46.956
un zey hobn g- m'iz gekumen shoyn akht a zeyger, nayn. s'iz geven blits meydlekh oykhet, daytshishe froyen oykh

00:05:47.181 --> 00:05:51.304
hot men undz geheysn, iz yeder mey- m'hot un- hobn mir gehat azoyne tep vos mir hobn genumen

00:05:51.304 --> 00:05:53.202
zup, milkh azoyne

00:05:53.202 --> 00:05:57.725
, az mir zaynen gegangen flegt aroysfaln di top un flegt er tsebrekhn alts.

00:05:57.725 --> 00:05:59.665
hot di daytshishe froyen gezogt di

00:05:59.665 --> 00:06:00.686
di ⟨blits⟩ meydlekh

00:06:00.686 --> 00:06:02.633
sharbns brengen glik

00:06:02.908 --> 00:06:04.981
az dos vet undz brengen glik.

00:06:04.225 --> 00:06:05.248
vos meynt dos?

00:06:04.981 --> 00:06:08.706
sharbns, dos heyst o- di, di tep

00:06:08.706 --> 00:06:10.986
vos me tsebrekht zikh vet brengen glik.

00:06:11.076 --> 00:06:13.179
azoy hobn zey geredt. ikh gedenk ⟨dos azoy⟩ vi haynt.

00:06:13.287 --> 00:06:16.740
un m'hot gezogt az UNK droysn oyfn apel, un ver es iz gezunt

00:06:16.763 --> 00:06:18.818
un ver es t- ho- ken geyn

00:06:18.818 --> 00:06:19.864
un hot shikh

00:06:19.864 --> 00:06:21.329
zol geyn mit undz.

00:06:21.387 --> 00:06:23.771
un der vos ken nit geyn zol blaybn in di barakn.

00:06:23.771 --> 00:06:24.992
zol blaybn oyf an ort.

00:06:25.318 --> 00:06:27.728
zey hobn aroys efsher a tsvey hundert fuftsik mentshn

00:06:27.728 --> 00:06:29.331
z- mit zey tsuzamen.

00:06:28.913 --> 00:06:30.493
un ir mit ayer shves-

00:06:29.331 --> 00:06:31.947
m'iz gegangen durkh an ander veg, nit

00:06:30.938 --> 00:06:33.497
ir mit ayer shvester?

00:06:31.947 --> 00:06:34.942
ikh mit mayn shvester, un a tsvey hundert fuftsik iz geven.

00:06:34.942 --> 00:06:36.470
nokh a meydl oykhet geven

00:06:36.470 --> 00:06:38.222
a Shavler geven

00:06:38.582 --> 00:06:42.823
un, un ikh UNK mit mi- oyfn veg gehat, nokh gehat nokh broyt shtiklekh a fule.

00:06:42.823 --> 00:06:45.900
ikh hob gefilt nit gut. m'iz shoyn bald krank gevorn.

00:06:45.973 --> 00:06:50.501
hob ikh getrakht az ⟨mir veln⟩ efsher bafrayt vern, di broyt vet blaybn, do kumen ⟨dokh⟩ rateven di mentshn

00:06:50.501 --> 00:06:51.781
hob ikh avekgegebn ir.

00:06:51.781 --> 00:06:53.589
hot zi gezogt UNK keyn mol nit fargesn.

00:06:53.589 --> 00:06:54.945
ikh veys nit tsi zi iz geblibn.

00:06:55.035 --> 00:06:56.830
un mir zaynen gegangen oyfn ve-

00:06:56.830 --> 00:06:59.660
mit zey, durkh an ander veg, nit oyf di veg vu forn.

00:06:59.660 --> 00:07:01.510
a hintershte veg hobn zey undz gefirt

00:07:01.545 --> 00:07:02.909
getribn, geyogt.

00:07:02.983 --> 00:07:04.479
esn hot men nit gegebn

00:07:04.924 --> 00:07:08.056
s- mir gegangen eyn tog oyfn marsh mit zey

00:07:08.097 --> 00:07:12.023
un mir zeen az mir forn durkh a dorf az di daytshn forn ahin

00:07:12.028 --> 00:07:13.557
forn tsurik

00:07:13.598 --> 00:07:16.359
u- un- kupes gantse ⟨do⟩ gehargete

00:07:16.450 --> 00:07:19.790
un, un di federn flien, azoy bay in geto geflit di federn

00:07:19.790 --> 00:07:21.780
azoy flit bay zey di federn

00:07:21.780 --> 00:07:22.538
iberal.

00:07:22.538 --> 00:07:25.050
un ⟨s'iz⟩ epes a gantse t-, a gantser tuml.

00:07:25.866 --> 00:07:29.170
ikh bin gegangen eyn tog hob ikh gegangen, bin ikh gegangen an ander tog.

00:07:29.170 --> 00:07:31.665
undz hot men arayngefirt in a shtal shlofn

00:07:31.873 --> 00:07:33.600
vu UNK di shtroy, di

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:34.866
shtroy, hey

00:07:34.866 --> 00:07:36.857
un zey zaynen gegangen in di hayzer shlofn.

00:07:36.857 --> 00:07:38.401
in di hayzer iz shoyn keyner nit geven.

00:07:38.401 --> 00:07:39.782
di glavne daytshn.

00:07:39.940 --> 00:07:43.258
dem tsveytn tog hobn zey vayter avekgefirt. s'iz geven bahaltn lebn a veldl

00:07:43.500 --> 00:07:45.350
un me darf undz vekn

00:07:45.373 --> 00:07:47.966
in der fri. keyner vekt undz nit oyfet.

00:07:48.394 --> 00:07:53.428
iz, ⟨vi⟩ mir hern fartog az ⟨m'iz⟩ geklapt, ⟨hot men⟩ geshrien eynem di andere. s'iz fintster

00:07:53.428 --> 00:07:57.281
m'iz hungerik. me veyst nit vu me leygt zikh in, in shtal arayn.

00:07:58.367 --> 00:08:00.288
in der fri hobn mir gehert iz gekumen a

00:08:00.288 --> 00:08:01.654
m'hot UNK shoyn reydn

00:08:01.654 --> 00:08:03.271
"OTKROYTE VOROTA."

00:08:03.295 --> 00:08:04.402
in rusish.

00:08:04.408 --> 00:08:05.954
"efnt oyf di toyer."

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:09.398
⟨hobn mir⟩ gevorn shtil ale. ikh ho- mir hobn farshtanen rusish

00:08:09.403 --> 00:08:10.986
di, di ungarishe ⟨nit⟩

00:08:10.986 --> 00:08:14.932
hot men gezogt "oy, 'OTKROYTE VOROTA,' epes a rusisher ⟨kol⟩."

00:08:15.073 --> 00:08:17.989
un m'hot zey oyfgerisn dem toyer, mit dem shlos

00:08:17.989 --> 00:08:20.116
un zey hobn gezogt "DEVOCHKI, VY SVOBODNY."

00:08:20.116 --> 00:08:21.989
hobn mir gemakht a groysn gvald.

00:08:21.081 --> 00:08:22.020
vos heyst?

00:08:21.989 --> 00:08:23.488
SVOBODNY ⟨heyst⟩ fray.

00:08:23.916 --> 00:08:27.032
hot, hobn mir gemakht a a groysn gvald. mir hobn geshrien

00:08:27.105 --> 00:08:29.090
hobn mir gemakht a groysn tuml

00:08:29.535 --> 00:08:32.313
UNK gezogt "shrayt nit un makht nit keyn tuml

00:08:30.784 --> 00:08:32.803
er hot geredt mit di soldatn?

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.439
un veynt nit."

00:08:33.439 --> 00:08:36.853
iz, i- s'iz a RAZVEDKA geven nokh ersht, oyf a

00:08:36.859 --> 00:08:38.999
"undzere veln ersht kumen bay nakht.

00:08:38.999 --> 00:08:42.623
di daytshn OTSTUPAYEN, un mir veln ersht kumen bay nakht. mir veln onkumen.

00:08:42.799 --> 00:08:45.797
makht nit keyn tuml, vayl me ken nokh itster oykhet aykh hargenen."

00:08:45.820 --> 00:08:48.919
