zi hot gehat shver, mayn shvester.

00:17:30.244 --> 00:17:31.706
s'iz geven a mishpokhe

00:17:31.813 --> 00:17:33.750
vos zey hobn ir tsugenumen take

00:17:33.750 --> 00:17:37.244
ober s'iz geven dortn, hobn zey m- goyim flegn araynkumen oyf ⟨zey⟩

00:17:37.244 --> 00:17:39.573
oyf esn, oyf trinken. zey hobn gehandlt

00:17:39.573 --> 00:17:42.062
flegt zi darfn vashn di padloges nokh dem

00:17:42.062 --> 00:17:45.172
un makhn reyn, iz zi dokh a kind, hot zi ⟨gevolt⟩ geyn in SCHOOL lernen

00:17:45.448 --> 00:17:49.509
nit gehat keyn gelt oyf koy- koyfn oyf, oyf lernen papir

00:17:49.667 --> 00:17:52.091
a bikhl. iz zi gegangen lernen, bay di rusishe dort.

00:17:52.350 --> 00:17:55.021
un, un s'iz gekumen zeyer a tokhter

00:17:55.021 --> 00:17:56.664
hot farlorn tsvey kinder

00:17:57.193 --> 00:17:59.448
a yingele in zelbn AGE vi mayn shvester.

00:17:59.488 --> 00:18:00.967
hot zi ge⟨UNK⟩ UNK

00:18:01.210 --> 00:18:04.157
az ir yingele iz umgekumen, un zi lebt

00:18:04.332 --> 00:18:08.159
un zi flegt vern meshuge in gantsn, flegt zi hakn di fentster.

00:18:08.159 --> 00:18:10.434
un oyf mayn shvester ⟨volt⟩ nit gehat keyn ort.

00:18:10.491 --> 00:18:12.673
un bay ir a yingele iz avekgegangen

00:18:12.673 --> 00:18:14.130
un mayn shvester lebt.

00:18:14.254 --> 00:18:16.239
hot zi gehat zeyer shlekht mit deroyf.

00:18:16.701 --> 00:18:18.298
ober ⟨zey hobn ir⟩ tsugeshribn

00:18:18.760 --> 00:18:21.330
zibn mentshn zaynen mir geven tsugeshribn oyf di papir

00:18:21.330 --> 00:18:23.287
un mayn balebos far avekgeyn

00:18:23.287 --> 00:18:25.034
mayn balebos di, di froy

00:18:25.034 --> 00:18:27.185
hot mir gegebn tsen DOLLAR mit zikh

00:18:27.185 --> 00:18:29.739
zi hot mir ayngeneyt in a kleydl UNK der pasik

00:18:29.779 --> 00:18:32.965
zogt zi "ikh gib dir tsen DOLLAR. bist geven an orntlekher kind

00:18:32.965 --> 00:18:35.460
un got zol dir fern, firn in a gute veg

00:18:36.478 --> 00:18:40.601
un, un andere" zogt zi "hobn a sakh gelt, kenen durkhfirn bay dir, ken men nokh trefn

00:18:40.601 --> 00:18:42.008
tsunemen di tsen DOLLAR."

00:18:42.283 --> 00:18:44.015
ikh hob dos nit geUSED di tsen DOLLAR.

00:18:44.359 --> 00:18:45.824
ye, azoy vi zi hot gezogt.

00:18:45.824 --> 00:18:48.116
nor zi not mir gegebn esn oyf a gantse vokh.

00:18:48.375 --> 00:18:50.204
zi hot mir ⟨gegebn⟩ broyt

00:18:50.204 --> 00:18:52.764
kez hot zi gemakht aleyn. zi hot milkh nit geUSED

00:18:52.768 --> 00:18:55.760
ongegebn a fule esn. ikh hob a gantse vokh gehat vos tsu esn.

00:18:55.834 --> 00:18:58.460
un nit nor mir aleyn zaynen geforn. polyakn zaynen oykh geforn.

00:18:58.467 --> 00:19:00.047
zey UNK ⟨oykh⟩ evakuirt.

00:19:00.120 --> 00:19:01.194
oyf Poyln.

00:19:01.302 --> 00:19:04.215
ale polyakn. der galekh, ale zaynen geforn.

00:19:04.238 --> 00:19:07.016
zey hobn gedarft durkhgeyn a grenets, dem rusishn grenets

00:19:07.663 --> 00:19:10.897
iz i- i- ho- hoyt men ⟨nokh⟩ getshepet tsu mayn shvester UNK

00:19:11.224 --> 00:19:13.912
vayl der shtempl geven ⟨oyf ire yorn, un⟩ zey hobn nit gezen.

00:19:13.912 --> 00:19:15.538
zogt er vet dir shikn tsurik.

00:19:15.713 --> 00:19:17.306
oy, a klog. vi vet ir shi-

00:19:17.306 --> 00:19:20.426
tsu vemen shikn tsurik? bin gegangen tsum galekh. der galekh iz oykh geforn.

00:19:20.426 --> 00:19:21.626
az vi vet ir shikn

00:19:21.626 --> 00:19:25.986
der galekh hot genumen betn zikh, a kleyne meydele, hot nit keyn eltern, vi vestu shikn eyner aleyn?

00:19:26.074 --> 00:19:28.349
UNK hob ikh gezogt ikh hob tsen DOLLAR

00:19:28.349 --> 00:19:30.556
hot men im gegebn tsen DOLLAR, hot er durkhgelozn.

00:19:31.373 --> 00:19:32.905
⟨azoy dos⟩ iz geven.

00:19:31.947 --> 00:19:33.274
gekumen tsum nuts.

00:19:32.905 --> 00:19:34.263
gekumen tsu nits, ye.

00:19:34.263 --> 00:19:36.997
di tsen DOLLAR, hot men durkhgelozn, di shvester ⟨iz⟩ avek mit mir.

00:19:36.997 --> 00:19:38.808
mir zaynen gekumen, ongekumen in Lodzh.

00:19:39.169 --> 00:19:40.803
ongekumen in Lodzh bin ikh a

00:19:40.803 --> 00:19:43.433
iz yidishe BRICHA hot gearbet zeyer gut

00:19:43.472 --> 00:19:45.828
zaynen gekumen UNK un gezukht

00:19:45.852 --> 00:19:47.955
mentshn vos kumen on fun di lagern.

00:19:48.028 --> 00:19:49.490
dan hobn zey undz geholfn.

00:19:49.868 --> 00:19:53.012
ANYWAY di mayne balebatim zaynen avekgeforn. zey hobn gehat gelt

00:19:53.012 --> 00:19:55.582
zey hobn undz ibergelozn aleyn, zey zogn zey kumen undz nemen.

00:19:55.588 --> 00:19:58.757
un mir veysn nit vi me fort in Lodzh, un on gelt

00:19:58.757 --> 00:20:01.052
vos tut men do? un di nakht falt tsu.

00:20:01.052 --> 00:20:03.128
iz gekumen fun yidishn komitet

00:20:03.128 --> 00:20:05.169
un yunge khevre iz geven tsvey

00:20:05.169 --> 00:20:07.989
zogn zey, ⟨mir hobn gezogt⟩ az mir zaynen fun di lagern gekumen

00:20:07.989 --> 00:20:10.969
zogt er "bar-, zayt ruik" zogt er

00:20:10.969 --> 00:20:12.839
"ikh kum bald mit mayn CAR

00:20:12.839 --> 00:20:15.934
un ikh fir aykh avek in ershtn bestn KIBUTS

00:20:15.990 --> 00:20:17.941
vu me est gut, me shloft gut.

00:20:17.982 --> 00:20:19.413
in DROR KIBUTS."

00:20:19.413 --> 00:20:20.712
⟨zikh⟩ ibergeredt

00:20:20.712 --> 00:20:23.932
un UNK bald take gekumen. zey hobn undz genumen avekgefirt in KIBUTS arayn.

00:20:24.327 --> 00:20:26.315
iz m- mir mit di shvester tsuzamen.

00:20:26.315 --> 00:20:27.645
in DROR kibuts.

00:20:27.499 --> 00:20:29.585
velkhe bavegung iz dos?

00:20:28.714 --> 00:20:30.429
in DROR, frayheyt.

00:20:30.655 --> 00:20:32.187
in dem KIBUTS hobn zey undz genumen.

00:20:32.187 --> 00:20:34.541
zey hobn gezogt az der KIBUTS halt zikh oys aleyn.

00:20:34.541 --> 00:20:36.548
mir arbetn ale, mir

00:20:36.548 --> 00:20:40.548
mir arbetn, ver s'iz shnayder, shuster, alerleyike fakhn

00:20:40.577 --> 00:20:42.371
un mir haltn zikh oys aleyn un

00:20:42.371 --> 00:20:44.402
un mir UNK geven nayntsn yor

00:20:44.425 --> 00:20:46.193
mir vet men oykh shikn tsu der arbet.

00:20:46.193 --> 00:20:48.775
ober mayn shvester, a kleyn meydele, hot er mir gezogt

00:20:48.775 --> 00:20:50.156
"iz nit gut far ir do.

00:20:50.365 --> 00:20:52.876
zi ken nokh lernen. zi ⟨iz in⟩ draytsnte yor

00:20:52.876 --> 00:20:54.716
un zi ken nokh lernen HEBREW

00:20:54.716 --> 00:20:57.326
un ⟨aher shoyn⟩ di kinder vet men shikn mit legale ALIYA.

00:20:57.435 --> 00:20:59.353
zol zi geyn in a ander KIBUTS."

00:20:59.376 --> 00:21:01.583
v- frier hobn mir nit gevelt,

00:21:01.583 --> 00:21:04.815
 tsesheydn zikh. mir geblibn lebn fun Hitlern, tsvey kinder

00:21:04.815 --> 00:21:07.993
iz e- iz e- er hot dos nokh azoy gezogt dem MADRICH

00:21:08.218 --> 00:21:12.464
dernokh zogt mayn shvester nokh a vokh arum, zi hot gesheylt kartofl do, far di mentshn in kikh

00:21:12.471 --> 00:21:14.611
zogt zi "Nekhame, veyst, ikh hob tsugenumen

00:21:14.611 --> 00:21:16.144
UNK mayn KIBUTS

00:21:16.217 --> 00:21:17.561
vu di kinder zaynen."

00:21:18.546 --> 00:21:20.669
zi iz avek dortn, hot zi gezen kinder

00:21:20.669 --> 00:21:24.618
vos zaynen oykh ts- i- di eltern zaynen ⟨umgekumen⟩ UNK fun Varshe

00:21:24.618 --> 00:21:27.248
kinder ⟨oykh⟩ geven bay goyim hot men undz oyfge- gekumen

00:21:27.248 --> 00:21:29.108
azoyne kinder iz geven a fule.

00:21:29.177 --> 00:21:31.508
un, un ir glaykhn, zogt zi

00:21:31.508 --> 00:21:34.288
"i- ikh blayb do in dem KIBUTS. me lernt

00:21:34.288 --> 00:21:36.363
un z- ale dem zelbn AGE vos ikh

00:21:36.363 --> 00:21:37.426
mayn glaykhn

00:21:37.426 --> 00:21:38.405
vil ikh geyn mit zey.

00:21:38.405 --> 00:21:39.375
⟨do⟩ blaybn mit zey."

00:21:39.375 --> 00:21:40.630
hobn mir zikh dan tsesheydt.

00:21:40.630 --> 00:21:43.890
un er hot gezogt mir az Yisroel iz a kleyn lendele, zol trefn in Yisroel.

00:21:43.909 --> 00:21:44.927
zi muz geyn

00:21:44.927 --> 00:21:46.909
in a legale ALIYA vet zi geyn, di kinder

00:21:46.909 --> 00:21:48.420
un me zol lernen HEBREW

00:21:48.420 --> 00:21:49.880
un m'vet zey gebn gute esn.

00:21:49.880 --> 00:21:51.328
zi darf nit arbetn nokh.

00:21:51.503 --> 00:21:53.049
vos hot ir geton?

00:21:52.752 --> 00:21:54.765
dos hobn mir geton, bin ikh geblibn shoyn

00:21:53.764 --> 00:21:55.935
vos, ir zayt geblibn

00:21:54.765 --> 00:21:56.393
ikh bin geblibn in dem KIBUTS.

00:21:56.393 --> 00:21:58.617
der KIBUTS iz geven akhtsik bokherim.

00:21:58.894 --> 00:22:01.160
gekumene fun Rusland soldatn nokh mit di

00:22:01.160 --> 00:22:02.610
mundirn, yidishe

00:22:02.826 --> 00:22:06.161
un s- un ⟨mit⟩ froyen ongekumen veynik. andere froyen zaynen krank geven

00:22:06.167 --> 00:22:07.817
un a por meydlekh iz geven.

00:22:07.817 --> 00:22:09.131
ale bokherim.

00:22:09.255 --> 00:22:11.426
un, un mener. ale mener.

00:22:11.483 --> 00:22:14.615
m- mir hobn gehert in Kelts iz geven a pogrom

00:22:15.263 --> 00:22:17.074
un di BRICHA flegt kumen tsu undz

00:22:17.074 --> 00:22:18.226
di Yisroeldike

00:22:18.283 --> 00:22:19.925
un zey hobn gehaltn lektsyes

00:22:19.925 --> 00:22:22.412
az mir on aykh kenen nit zayn.

00:22:22.553 --> 00:22:24.504
mir muzn hobn aykh.

00:22:24.983 --> 00:22:27.997
m- on aykh, mir muzn boy- hobn an eygene land.

00:22:28.459 --> 00:22:29.450
ale

00:22:29.450 --> 00:22:33.310
vi eyne, mir geyen ale nokh Yisroel. mir geyen di umlegale UNK. mir muzn

00:22:33.310 --> 00:22:35.591
hobn an eygn land. mir muzn kemfn far dem.

00:22:35.614 --> 00:22:38.223
on aykh kenen mir nit zayn. mir muzn ay- mir darfn aykh hobn.

00:22:38.618 --> 00:22:40.839
azoy ⟨hot shoyn⟩ geredt durkhoys azoyne zakhn

00:22:40.862 --> 00:22:45.311
un mir hobn geven in, mir hobn gehert az s'iz do a Keltser pogrom gevorn

00:22:45.385 --> 00:22:49.159
zaynen zey gekumen, un m'iz geshtanen mit UNK. m'hot gehit. m'hot gehat gever

00:22:49.182 --> 00:22:52.064
un m'hot gezogt az es kenen kumen unterhargenen dem KIBUTS.

00:22:52.064 --> 00:22:53.917
akhtsik bokherim, me zarf zey hobn.

00:22:54.025 --> 00:22:56.449
iz ho- hot men gegebn a bafel

00:22:56.573 --> 00:22:59.014
BRICHA, hot dos gearbet, di Yisroeldike

00:22:59.037 --> 00:23:01.494
az mir zoln geyn nokh Es- nokh Italye.

00:23:01.821 --> 00:23:02.912
Italye.

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:05.493
di umlegale ALIYA. dos iz geven in zeks un fertsikster yor.

00:23:06.040 --> 00:23:07.924
⟨beys⟩ Yisroel iz nokh nit geven Yisroel.

00:23:08.368 --> 00:23:09.470
avek ⟨afile ge-⟩

00:23:09.470 --> 00:23:12.329
mit di ALIYA. mir zaynen gegangen oyf di, oyf di

00:23:12.329 --> 00:23:15.109
der, der MADRICH hot gezogt on kinder

00:23:15.140 --> 00:23:17.342
un di mener zoln shlofn mit di vayber

00:23:17.342 --> 00:23:20.124
vayle m- me darf geyn oyf berg, oyf hoykhe berg.

00:23:20.198 --> 00:23:23.094
un me, un m'vet nemen, durkhmakhn a shvere veg.

00:23:24.130 --> 00:23:24.934
mir

00:23:25.007 --> 00:23:26.587
mir zaynen gekumen

00:23:26.796 --> 00:23:30.249
oyf di, oyf di berg, aroyfgekrokhn shoyn koym mit tsores

00:23:30.340 --> 00:23:33.518
iz, iz der pastekh, i- der vos fir- pashet di

00:23:33.518 --> 00:23:34.948
di shepsn, di beheymes

00:23:34.948 --> 00:23:37.707
hot er gezen az es geyen a sakh mentshn

00:23:37.900 --> 00:23:39.531
hot er gemasert undz.

00:23:39.823 --> 00:23:41.533
di, gezogt az

00:23:41.533 --> 00:23:43.883
az me geyt epes, s'iz a umlegale veg

00:23:43.907 --> 00:23:45.656
hot men undz alemen gekert tsurik.

00:23:45.831 --> 00:23:47.090
nit gelozn geyn.

00:23:47.383 --> 00:23:48.693
zaynen mir arayngegangen in

00:23:48.693 --> 00:23:51.333
in Estraykh in an ander lager, BET BIALIK

00:23:51.354 --> 00:23:54.043
un mir zaynen dortn geven biz vanet me vet kenen forn nokh Yisroel.

00:23:54.505 --> 00:23:56.063
vu hot ir ah

00:23:56.063 --> 00:23:57.823
zikh bakent mit ayer man?

00:23:57.306 --> 00:23:58.582
in Estraykh.

00:23:58.639 --> 00:23:59.915
in BET BIALIK?

00:23:59.500 --> 00:24:01.007
in BET BIALIK. er iz ge-

00:24:01.007 --> 00:24:02.635
dem maynem hob ikh gekent

00:24:02.635 --> 00:24:04.117
ven ikh bin shoyn gekumen aheym.

00:24:04.107 --> 00:24:06.025
ah vi, vi heyst ayer man?

00:24:05.811 --> 00:24:06.952
Ayzik.

00:24:07.195 --> 00:24:08.522
Ayzik...

00:24:07.532 --> 00:24:09.601
ikh hob im gekent ven er iz gekumen aheym.

00:24:09.102 --> 00:24:10.750
Ayzik BOGOT.

00:24:09.692 --> 00:24:11.350
er iz, er iz geven

00:24:11.350 --> 00:24:14.560
g- geblibn lebn UNK al pi nes fun di

00:24:14.560 --> 00:24:15.468
partizaner.

00:24:15.468 --> 00:24:16.689
er iz antlofn gevorn.

00:24:17.337 --> 00:24:20.891
iz, iz er gekumen a- un dernokh hot men im tsugenumen in militer.

00:24:20.998 --> 00:24:23.219
er iz bafrayt gevorn in finf un fertsikstn yor, mayn man

00:24:23.378 --> 00:24:26.970
iz e- iz er gekumen tsu zayne a tante, un di tante hot zikh gefunen

00:24:26.970 --> 00:24:29.060
in mayn shtetl vu ikh bin geven gekumen.

00:24:29.419 --> 00:24:31.635
iz e- hot zi im ge- tsugenumen tsu zikh.

00:24:31.635 --> 00:24:35.556
⟨nor er iz⟩ geven a shnayder, hot er geneyt a bisl, di mentshn, geven, opgerisn

00:24:35.612 --> 00:24:38.390
hob ikh im ge- hob ikh im gekent fun d- UNK tante.

00:24:38.464 --> 00:24:41.495
hob ikh dan getrakht "oy, ven er hot mit mir khasene

00:24:41.788 --> 00:24:45.742
ven ikh, iz er a bal melokhe, ikh volt gehat an ort vu tsu zayn."

00:24:45.742 --> 00:24:47.604
kh'hob gedarft zayn bay fremde mentshn.

00:24:47.661 --> 00:24:50.577
farshteyt? nor nit er hot getrakht, nit ikh hob getrakht.

00:24:50.577 --> 00:24:52.903
er, er hot gezogt er geyt oykh avek nokh Poyln.

00:24:52.926 --> 00:24:55.164
ale hobn gezogt, dem zelbn gedank gehat.

00:24:55.221 --> 00:24:56.548
me geyt nokh Yisroel.

00:24:56.875 --> 00:24:59.031
k- ale vos UNK gekumen

00:24:59.031 --> 00:25:01.053
hobn mir gezogt mir boyen do nit keyn lebn mer.

00:25:01.060 --> 00:25:02.398
mir geyen nokh Yisroel.

00:25:02.398 --> 00:25:04.027
der eyntsiker veg iz dos.

00:25:04.027 --> 00:25:04.851
ale.

00:25:05.143 --> 00:25:06.807
nu, iz ah

00:25:07.607 --> 00:25:09.882
vi az- vi azoy zayt ir gekumen

00:25:09.835 --> 00:25:11.569
in Amerike?

00:25:09.882 --> 00:25:11.600
aroys fun ah

00:25:11.569 --> 00:25:12.900
fun Estraykh?

00:25:12.400 --> 00:25:13.102
fun

00:25:13.108 --> 00:25:15.650
e- mayn shvester iz geven in di amerikaner zone

00:25:15.792 --> 00:25:17.130
in INDERSDORF

00:25:17.130 --> 00:25:19.281
bay di Menashkes, hot men gehat far zey a

00:25:19.281 --> 00:25:20.176
a

00:25:20.176 --> 00:25:23.329
gehat gut. m'hot gegebn zey esn shokolad, m'hot gelernt

00:25:23.385 --> 00:25:26.025
un m'hot gezogt az di kinder firt, fun UNK ⟨legal⟩.

00:25:26.025 --> 00:25:27.495
m'hot zey gefi- UNK tsu firn durkh

00:25:27.495 --> 00:25:28.610
durkh Frankraykh.

00:25:28.650 --> 00:25:33.588
un ikh bin ge- hob ikh gevel- bin ikh geven in Estraykh, un dernokh hob ikh geha- UNK farbindung mit di shvester mayne

00:25:33.612 --> 00:25:36.308
un mit di tante geven in, oyf di amerikaner zone

00:25:36.308 --> 00:25:39.801
hobn zey gezogt tsu mir az du host gornisht nit. me darf UNK dortn zayn

00:25:39.801 --> 00:25:40.586
kum

00:25:40.586 --> 00:25:41.902
in amerikaner zone.

00:25:41.902 --> 00:25:43.797
fun danet iz gikher tsu avekgeyn.

00:25:43.956 --> 00:25:46.785
bin ikh gekumen tsu mayn shvester, hob ikh getrofn ir

00:25:47.213 --> 00:25:49.316
ibergenekhtikt in Minkhn

00:25:49.339 --> 00:25:54.007
koym mit tsore gekumen tsu mayn shve- der KIBUTS hot mir aroysgelozn, hot er mir gegebn a pekl tsigaretn

00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:55.138
mer gornisht.

00:25:55.313 --> 00:25:57.520
un mit dem pekl tsigaretn hob ikh gedarft

00:25:57.520 --> 00:26:00.490
hob ikh gezen a, a politsyant iz geshtanen, hob ikh im gegebn

00:26:00.490 --> 00:26:04.048
i- tsigaretn, zol mir gebn gelt oyf tsu forn mitn TRAI- mitn TRAIN.

00:26:04.375 --> 00:26:06.396
ikh hob gornisht nit gehat vos UNK

00:26:06.396 --> 00:26:09.147
tomer vet mir trefn di amerikaner UNK

00:26:09.147 --> 00:26:10.157
handl dokh nit.

00:26:10.517 --> 00:26:13.953
ikh bin gekumen in amerikaner zone, ⟨bin⟩ gekumen mayn shvester ⟨ir bazukhn⟩

00:26:14.027 --> 00:26:15.506
hot tsu mir azoy gezogt

00:26:15.917 --> 00:26:19.454
"du zolst geyn dayn veg vu dayn kop diktirt dir.

00:26:20.119 --> 00:26:23.336
ikh vel geyn in di veg vu mayn kop diktirt mir.

00:26:23.359 --> 00:26:25.423
du zest ale geyen nokh Yisroel.

00:26:25.423 --> 00:26:26.874
ikh gey mit zey mit.

00:26:26.874 --> 00:26:27.684
keyn a-

00:26:27.684 --> 00:26:29.580
nit ikh vil zayn bay an onkl.

00:26:29.923 --> 00:26:32.552
nit ikh vil zayn bay dir az du vest khasene hobn.

00:26:32.552 --> 00:26:33.882
ikh gey nokh Yisroel.

00:26:34.210 --> 00:26:35.800
un mir hobn zikh tsesheydt dan.

00:26:35.931 --> 00:26:37.505
bin ikh a- ikh bin avek fun ir.

00:26:37.505 --> 00:26:39.502
kh'hob nokh nit gekent zayn. ⟨s'iz dokh⟩ ale kinder.

00:26:39.930 --> 00:26:41.758
avek ikh bin nokh in KIBUTS.

00:26:41.758 --> 00:26:43.434
mit di tante bin ikh geven.

00:26:43.440 --> 00:26:44.829
gekumen tsu di tante

00:26:44.829 --> 00:26:46.319
do, un mayn man

00:26:46.444 --> 00:26:50.049
hot a gehat a, a, a ot der, a tante

00:26:51.118 --> 00:26:53.165
un zi hot zikh farbundn mit dem onkl

00:26:53.165 --> 00:26:54.583
der vos iz geblibn fun

00:26:54.583 --> 00:26:57.052
fun Nementshin, fun grub aroys.

00:26:57.447 --> 00:26:59.989
un er hot gehat a shvester in, in Pariz.

00:27:00.349 --> 00:27:03.307
hot er adurkhgeshribn mit di shvester, hot di shvester gezogt

00:27:03.307 --> 00:27:05.169
az er zol kumen nokh Pariz.

00:27:05.833 --> 00:27:08.122
in Pariz v- ir bruder hot zi gevelt.

00:27:08.162 --> 00:27:10.926
iz, hot, un mayn man iz geven mit di tante

00:27:10.926 --> 00:27:13.370
iz tsulib di tante iz er gekumen oykh nokh Pariz.

00:27:13.714 --> 00:27:16.222
lomir iberbaytn di tashme nokh a mol.

00:27:14.389 --> 00:27:15.212
ye.

00:27:15.212 --> 00:27:16.031
nu?

00:27:16.031 --> 00:27:17.538
un dos iz geven di historye.

00:27:17.545 --> 00:27:18.298
UNK

00:27:17.545 --> 00:27:18.939
shoyn geendikt?

00:27:18.810 --> 00:27:19.431
yo.

00:27:19.431 --> 00:27:22.380
mir UNK hern nokh a

00:27:22.380 --> 00:27:25.710
a kurtse derklerung fun aykh UNK iberbaytn di tashme.

00:27:23.170 --> 00:27:24.540
ye. ye.
